<br />I imagine that any programming discussion in the new sub-forum would be related to animations, effects (raster or otherwise), things like that. The things you mentioned are part of the game logic, and should be discussed in the NESDEV sub-forum.
<br />
<br />I'm not sure what to expect of the new sub-forum though. Whether it will be more visual or more technical remains to be seen.

		

