<br />For example, I'd want to share NES Graphics between the NES and Game Boy sections, given how similar the capabilities of NES and GBC are.
<br />
<br />"A place for your artistic side. Discuss techniques and tools for pixel art on the NES, GBC, and similar platforms."
<br />
<br />EDIT: The first topic I'll move into the new section is probably <a href="http://nesdev.com/bbs/viewtopic.php?t=6004" class="postlink">the one that dissected CV3 and Faxanadu</a>.

		

